{"word":"H3076 - יְהֹוחָנָן - Yᵉhôwchânân - yeh-ho-khaw-nawn' - Jehohanan","slug":"H3076","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">יְהֹוחָנָן</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>Yᵉhôwchânân"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>yeh-ho-khaw-nawn'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Jehohanan"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"Original: <b><he>יהוחנן</he></b> <p />Transliteration: <b>yehôchânân</b> <p />Phonetic: <b>yeh-ho-khaw-nawn'</b> <p class=\"bdb_def\"><b>BDB Definition</b>:</p> Jehohanan = \"Jehovah has graced\" <ol><li>a Korhite Levite and one of the doorkeepers to the tabernacle in the time of David</li><li>a captain of Judah under king Jehoshaphat</li><li>a priest during the high priesthood of Joiakim who returned with Zerubbabel</li><li>a high priest in the time of Ezra</li><li>a Levite priest who took part in the dedication of the wall in the time of Nehemiah</li><li>son of Tobiah</li><li>an Ephraimite</li><li>an Israelite with a foreign wife in the time of Ezra</li><li>a Jewish captain after the fall of Jerusalem<ol type='a'><li>the eldest son of king Josiah</li><li>a post-exilic prince of the line of David</li><li>father of Azariah, priest in Solomon's time</li><li>a Benjamite, one of David's mighty warriors</li><li>a Gadite, one of David's mighty warriors</li><li>a returning exile</li></ol></li></ol> <p />Origin: from <a href=\"#/H3068\">H3068</a> and <a href=\"#/H2603\">H2603</a> <p />TWOT entry: None <p />Part(s) of speech: Proper Name Masculine "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1933\">H1933</a>, <a href=\"#/H1942\">H1942</a>, <a href=\"#/H1943\">H1943</a>, <a href=\"#/H1944\">H1944</a>, <a href=\"#/H1953\">H1953</a>, <a href=\"#/H1962\">H1962</a>, <a href=\"#/H3050\">H3050</a>, <a href=\"#/H3058\">H3058</a>, <a href=\"#/H3059\">H3059</a>, <a href=\"#/H3060\">H3060</a>, <a href=\"#/H3068\">H3068</a>, <a href=\"#/H3069\">H3069</a>, <a href=\"#/H3075\">H3075</a>, <a href=\"#/H3077\">H3077</a>, <a href=\"#/H3078\">H3078</a>, <a href=\"#/H3079\">H3079</a>, <a href=\"#/H3080\">H3080</a>, <a href=\"#/H3081\">H3081</a>, <a href=\"#/H3082\">H3082</a>, <a href=\"#/H3083\">H3083</a>, <a href=\"#/H3085\">H3085</a>, <a href=\"#/H3086\">H3086</a>, <a href=\"#/H3087\">H3087</a>, <a href=\"#/H3088\">H3088</a>, <a href=\"#/H3089\">H3089</a>, <a href=\"#/H3090\">H3090</a>, <a href=\"#/H3091\">H3091</a>, <a href=\"#/H3092\">H3092</a>, <a href=\"#/H3097\">H3097</a>, <a href=\"#/H3098\">H3098</a>, <a href=\"#/H3099\">H3099</a>, <a href=\"#/H3100\">H3100</a>, <a href=\"#/H3101\">H3101</a>, <a href=\"#/H3107\">H3107</a>, <a href=\"#/H3108\">H3108</a>, <a href=\"#/H3110\">H3110</a>, <a href=\"#/H3111\">H3111</a>, <a href=\"#/H3112\">H3112</a>, <a href=\"#/H3113\">H3113</a>, <a href=\"#/H3114\">H3114</a>, <a href=\"#/H3115\">H3115</a>, <a href=\"#/H3116\">H3116</a>, <a href=\"#/H3122\">H3122</a>, <a href=\"#/H3129\">H3129</a>, <a href=\"#/H3133\">H3133</a>, <a href=\"#/H3134\">H3134</a>, <a href=\"#/H3135\">H3135</a>, <a href=\"#/H3136\">H3136</a>, <a href=\"#/H3137\">H3137</a>, <a href=\"#/H3141\">H3141</a>, <a href=\"#/H3146\">H3146</a>, <a href=\"#/H3147\">H3147</a>, <a href=\"#/H3442\">H3442</a>, <a href=\"#/H3659\">H3659</a>"}]}